I give them feedback
that helps them

00:02:23.050 --> 00:02:23.980
achieve their goals.

00:02:23.980 --> 00:02:26.760
And that's the goals for that
session, the goals for that

00:02:26.760 --> 00:02:27.560
training cycle.

00:02:27.560 --> 00:02:29.800
And ultimately the goals that
will get them towards elite

00:02:29.800 --> 00:02:31.870
performance, and hopefully
an Olympic medal.

